				"description": "Submits a new inquiry from the public inquiry form. No authentication required.\n\n**Request Body:**\n- clientName (string, required): Full name of the client\n- contactNo (string, required): 10-digit mobile number\n- email (string, required): Valid email address\n- occasionType (string, required): Type of event (Wedding, Birthday, Corporate, etc.)\n- numberOfGuests (number, required): Expected number of guests\n- eventStartDateTime (ISO string, required): Event start date and time\n- eventEndDateTime (ISO string, required): Event end date and time\n\n**Validation:**\n- contactNo must be 10 digits\n- email must be valid format\n- eventEndDateTime must be after eventStartDateTime\n- numberOfGuests must be positive number"
			},
